description:
This match was shot LIVE on Noveber 15th as is already getting a lot of buzz. Jayogen has been rocking season 11. In her first singles match ever she took on Bella Rossi in an extremely close bout. Today she sees Penny Barber as just another stepping stone on her way to taking on the Champ for the Belt.
Penny Barber doesn't consider herself to be one of the "better" wrestlers. She falls short in round 1 but her tenacity and shit talk skills give her an advantage going forward after the first round. This is one of the most dominant Cum From Behind victories ever seen on the US mats.
title: Two Strong Welter Weight Babes Battle for the chance to fuck the champ
